De_BlueCorridor_Kai - Bomb/Defuse
by Schuzak
5/May/2009


More fps-friendly version of de_BlueCorridor.

Changes:
*Fixed stucking area.
*Deleted HDR capability.
*Deleted refract shader materials.
*Removed all models.
*Reduced spawn points. Now Ts can quick start off.


1, Description

A terrorists group is attacking a museum in Tokyo.

Counter-Terrorists:
Save important cultural assets or eliminate all terrorists.

Terrorists:
Blast one of two bombsites.


2, Installation

Just extract .BSP file into the maps folder. All required files (.NAV, radar map, materials etc.) are included in .BSP.
